OL,3,CPupils trekking miles for lessons
OL,4,Cshows need for more teachers, Lib Dems
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe Scottish Government has been urged
OL,8,Fto do more to address falling teacher
OL,9,Fnumbers, as figures show increasing
OL,10,Fnumbers of pupils are having to "trek
OL,11,Fmiles" for lessons in key subjects.
OL,13,FAccording to figures obtained by the
OL,14,FLiberal Democrats through a freedom of
OL,15,Finformation request, 1,599 pupils were
OL,16,Faffected by "consortia arrangements"
OL,17,Fbetween schools in the 2023/24
OL,18,Facademic year, up from 1,468 the year
OL,19,Fbefore.
