OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FConsortia arrangements enable pupils
OL,8,Fto travel to a different school for
OL,9,Flessons that are not offered at their
OL,10,Fown school.
OL,12,FThe figures show some pupils in
OL,13,FAberdeenshire, Dumfries and Galloway,
OL,14,FEast Lothian, Orkney, Perth and
OL,15,FKinross, Scottish Borders and South
OL,16,FAyrshire travelled more than 10 miles
OL,17,Ffor lessons in a number of subjects.
