OL,3,CPupils trekking miles for lessons
OL,4,Cshows need for more teachers, Lib Dems
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThis included pupils in the Borders
OL,8,Ftravelling up to 12 miles for advanced
OL,9,Fhigher physics, maths and history
OL,10,Flessons, and pupils in Dumfries and
OL,11,FGalloway travelling 20 miles for
OL,12,Fadvanced higher religious, moral and
OL,13,Fphilosophical studies lessons.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, pupils in East Lothian had
OL,16,Fto travel 23 miles for business skills
OL,17,Flessons.
OL,19,FThe number of of consortia
OL,20,Farrangements also rose from 399 in
OL,21,F2022/23 to 471 last year.
