OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FLiberal Democrat education
OL,8,Fspokesperson Willie Rennie said the
OL,9,Ffigures showed there were "not enough
OL,10,Fteachers in key subjects".
OL,12,F"The SNP once claimed that education
OL,13,Fwould be their defining mission.
OL,14,FInstead, it has become their defining
OL,15,Ffailure," he said.
OL,17,F"On their watch, young people are
OL,18,Fhaving to trek miles and miles to
OL,19,Fattend lessons in key subjects.
