OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"These journeys take up huge chunks of
OL,8,Fthe school day, precious time that
OL,9,Fcould be better spent learning or
OL,10,Fengaging in extracurricular
OL,11,Factivities."
OL,13,F"There are not enough teachers in key
OL,14,Fsubjects. By failing to promote
OL,15,Fteaching as a rewarding career, the
OL,16,FSNP are denying young people the
OL,17,Fguidance and support they need,
OL,18,Fespecially in more rural and remote
OL,19,Fcommunities.
