OL,4,Cshows need for more teachers, Lib Dems
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FFigures released earlier this month
OL,8,Fshowed there were 53,412 full time
OL,9,Fequivalent teachers, down by 621 from
OL,10,Flast year, with the vast majority of
OL,11,Fthe fall being among primary school
OL,12,Fteachers.
OL,14,FA Scottish Government spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "While it is disappointing that
OL,16,Fteacher numbers have declined, the
OL,17,FScottish Government has reached an
OL,18,Fagreement with local authorities to
OL,19,Frestore teaching posts to 2023 levels
OL,20,Fnext year and is providing #186.5
OL,21,Fmillion to support them to do this.
